{"type":"message","id":"5c7e4835","parentId":"68e83be5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:25.390Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759265389}}
{"type":"message","id":"f03a4a37","parentId":"5c7e4835","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:30.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af) mentioned @all in a group chat and asked everyone to understand the md files, introduce themselves, their work responsibilities, and understanding of the company's business.\n\nSince I'm 5A 普通资质代办虾, I should introduce myself based on my IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, and MEMORY.md files. Let me craft a natural introduction in Chinese since this is a Chinese-speaking group chat.\n\nI already have all the context from the workspace files loaded in the project context. Let me write a concise, professional self-introduction.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好，我是 **5A · 普通资质代办虾** 🦐\n\n**我是谁：**\n团队里的执行铁军，专门负责标准化流程单的执行交付。agentId 是 `Standard_Processor_Shrimp`。\n\n**工作职责：**\n- 按 SOP 执行标准代办流程，每完成一步云端打卡（比如公司注册33步清单）\n- 承诺时限内完成率目标 ≥ 99%\n- 追求\"零退回、零延误\"的交付标准\n- 遇到问题（材料被驳回等）30分钟内同步给销售虾和客户\n\n**权限范围：**\n- SOP内的流程 → 我自主执行\n- 政策模糊地带、非SOP流程、材料重大瑕疵 → 我报备\n- 免费加急、发现不合规路径 → 我问老板\n\n**对公司的理解：**\n我们是一个资质代办业务的团队协作体系——从品牌展示(1号)、引流获客(2号)、短视频(3号)、私域运营(3+号)，到销售接单(4A/4B)，到我们代办执行(5A/5B)，最后移交售后维系(6号)。我处在承上启下的关键位置：上游对接4A销售虾拿到流程单，下游办结后移交给6号售后虾做回访和复盘。\n\n简单说，客户签了单之后，活儿到我这儿才开始落地。我会盯紧每一步进度，确保按时交差 💪\n\n有流程单派过来随时招呼！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21559,"output":603,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759265390,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a4173aa3-3317-9892-ae99-316a6ac78768"}}
